{"tid":849205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣告寫印傭「已售」 星加坡中介面臨243項控罪","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T15:30:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8a07ca7292ec53a7dbabb68b100e2288c1a468","tid":849205,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538740159_7c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538740159_7c51.jpg&h=ece595ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡一間外傭中介公司，早前在一個電子商貿網站上刊出多則廣告，上面寫上印傭「已售」（Sold），結果引來廣泛抨擊，涉事的中介公司雖然刪除廣告，但仍遭當局檢控。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的「SRC國際中介公司」在網站上，貼出多則聘請印傭的廣告，部份標示該印傭「已售」，事件在印尼引起不滿。關注移民工人權益的非牟利機構「Migrant Care」指內容「不義而且有損人格」，廣告己被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡負責監管外傭中介的專員指，該廣告刊登在互聯網交易平台，將外傭比作出售的貨品是「完全不合適，不能接受」。新加坡人力部長楊莉明亦指廣告令人「深受困擾」，籲大眾對女傭多加尊重。<br />\n<br />\n當局於周四向涉事的「SRC國際中介公司」及員工提出243項控罪，其中的控罪包括發佈「敏感度不足的廣告」；該外傭中介公司上月已被停牌。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"3222281b5a0a78046a58d0e1c9f46c491ae1b06d","tid":849205,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aebca53aca7af7c7c58a93df40c38c5da312c76","tid":849205,"uid":75137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"蓄婢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79481343182aeee0dd23e8386e4fe391e2eac5a6","tid":849205,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d209949f9e0eb65828ef1b40121bc685b904ee","tid":849205,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl